# Wiring Reference

## 1. Basic Setup — Soil Moisture + Relay + Solenoid Valve

```
Arduino Uno                  Soil Moisture Sensor
───────────                  ────────────────────
   A0        ◄──────────────  AOUT (Analog Output)
   5V        ──────────────►  VCC
   GND       ──────────────►  GND


Arduino Uno                  Relay Module
───────────                  ────────────
   Pin 2     ──────────────►  IN  (Signal)
   5V        ──────────────►  VCC
   GND       ──────────────►  GND

Relay Module                 Solenoid Valve
────────────                 ──────────────
   COM       ──────────────►  One terminal of valve
   NO        ──────────────►  Power supply (+)
                              Other terminal → GND
```

> **NO** = Normally Open terminal. The solenoid valve energizes (opens) when the relay closes the circuit.

